headline: Casella-operated New York landfill to close in 2028; Republic appeals Tennessee expansion denial
summary: Current or proposed landfills in Arizona, Hawai’i, Michigan, New Jersey, Pennsylvania and Virginia had recent updates on permitting and other projects. This includes sites operated by WM, GFL Environmental and others.
